description: The AMUNDI PHYSICAL GOLD ETC offers investors exposure to the movements of the gold spot price. The ETC provides investors with a liquid, flexible and cost efficient way to invest in physical gold. The ETC is backed by physically allocated gold, which is held by HSBC Bank Plc (the custodian). Each physical bar is held in a segregated account, individually identified and allocated.
name: AMUNDI PHYSICAL GOLD ETC (C)
